📬 n8n SMTP Email Setup: Visual Workflow Guide
Here’s what you need:

🧩 Workflow Nodes
csharp
Copy
Edit
[Trigger Node (e.g., Webhook / Cron)]
        ↓
[Email Send Node (SMTP)]
✅ Step-by-Step Setup
1️⃣ Add a Trigger Node
Use any of these:

Cron → To send daily summary emails.

Webhook → To trigger alerts from your analysis agents.

2️⃣ Add “Email Send” Node
🛠️ Basic Setup:
Mode: SMTP

SMTP Host: smtp.gmail.com (or Outlook / custom provider)

SMTP Port: 587 (for TLS) or 465 (for SSL)

Secure: ✅ true (for Gmail, use SSL or TLS)

User: your.email@gmail.com

Password: your_app_password (NOT your Gmail login — use App Passwords)

💌 Email Details:
From Email: your.email@gmail.com

To Email: recipient@example.com (or dynamic like from a parameter)

Subject: 🚨 Stock Alert: {{ $json.symbol }}

Text:

txt
Copy
Edit
Hey Trader,

Here's your stock alert for {{ $json.symbol }}:

Signal: {{ $json.signal }}
Sentiment: {{ $json.sentiment }}

📈📉 Happy Trading!
🧠 Sample Input Data (for test run)
From a previous node (e.g., Analysis Agent), you might pass:

json
Copy
Edit
{
  "symbol": "TSLA",
  "signal": "Buy - RSI < 30",
  "sentiment": "Positive"
}
🔗 Example Workflow (JSON Export)
Here’s a copy-paste-ready n8n workflow snippet you can import:

📄 stock_alert_email.json (Short version)
json
Copy
Edit
{
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {},
      "id": "trigger",
      "name": "Cron Trigger",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.cron",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [250, 300],
      "parameters": {
        "triggerTimes": [
          {
            "mode": "everyX",
            "value": 10,
            "unit": "minutes"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "fromEmail": "your.email@gmail.com",
        "toEmail": "recipient@gmail.com",
        "subject": "🚨 Stock Alert: {{ $json.symbol }}",
        "text": "Signal: {{ $json.signal }}\nSentiment: {{ $json.sentiment }}",
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "email",
      "name": "Send Email",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.emailSend",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [500, 300],
      "credentials": {
        "smtp": {
          "id": "your-cred-id",
          "name": "Gmail SMTP"
        }
      }
    }
  ],
  "connections": {
    "Cron Trigger": {
      "main": [
        [
          {
            "node": "Send Email",
            "type": "main",
            "index": 0
          }
        ]
      ]
    }
  }
}
To import:

Click on 🧠 “Import” on the top right corner in n8n

Paste the JSON above

Replace your.email@gmail.com, recipient@gmail.com, and set the SMTP credentials in the Email node.

🔐 Credentials Setup (1-time)
Go to Credentials → SMTP

Click New Credentials

Fill:

Host: smtp.gmail.com

Port: 465 or 587

User: your.email@gmail.com

Password: App Password from Google

Then attach it to the Email Node in the workflow.

Let me know if:

You want to send HTML email

You want to attach PDF or chart reports

You want conditional alerts (like RSI < 30 only)
